translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: モテ力で俺に勝とうなど、十億年早いわ！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Trying to beat me with charm? You're a billion years too early!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 一行は、そのまま別室へと消えた。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The group disappeared straight into another room.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ……この声……サイアスね
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: ...This voice... it's Saiasu.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 羽目を外して…………ずいぶん、お楽しみみたい。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: They're really letting loose... seems to be enjoying themselves a lot.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ゼスの恥にならなければ……まぁ、いいけど
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: As long as they're not bringing shame to Zeth... well, it's fine.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 身体が、勝手に沈む。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: My body sinks involuntarily.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 口元まで、心地よい湯の中に沈んでいく。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I sink into the pleasant water up to my mouth.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ………………ばかもの
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: ...Fool.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ぶくぶくと泡立つ音に紛れて、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Muddled within the bubbling sound,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: その呟きは夜気に消えていった。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: That whisper vanished into the night air.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 仕方ないか。では、私も前線に出るわね
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It can’t be helped. Then, I’ll head to the front lines as well.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: こんにちは。失礼するわね
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hello. Excuse me.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あ、千鶴子様。いらっしゃいませ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ah, Lady Chizuruko. Welcome.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あっ……あの方……山田千鶴子さん、ですよね？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ah... That person... is Yamada Chizuruko, right?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そうですね。ゼス四天王筆頭……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: That's right. The leader of the Zeth Four Heavenly Kings...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ゼスの内政、軍事、外交全てを司る、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The one who controls Zeth's internal affairs, military, and diplomacy,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 事実上の頂点……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The de facto pinnacle...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: こっちの資料、運んできたわよ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I brought these materials over here.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 国内情勢と軍の現状、それにゼスに来てる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The domestic situation and current state of the military, plus the status of demon troops in Zeth,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔軍の状況分析
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: an analysis of the demon army's status.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 助かります。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: That helps a lot.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 千鶴子様にわざわざ来てもらってすみません
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Sorry for making Lady Chizuruko come all the way here.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 私がやった方が最終的に手間が省けるから。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It's ultimately less work if I do it myself.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ……今日はこのままとんぼ返りだけど
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: ...But today I'll just make a quick return trip like this.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ありがとうございます……お疲れ様です
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Thank you... and good work.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 苦笑しあう二人の後ろでは、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Behind the two sharing a wry smile,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 紙が満載された大量の箱が、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Boxes brimming with paper,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ゼス兵たちによって次から次へと運び込まれていく。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: were carried in one after another by Zeth soldiers.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: すみません、ウルザ殿。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Excuse me, Lord Urza.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 頂いた資料、処理に掛かって宜しいでしょうか。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: May I begin processing the materials you provided?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 半日ほどで出来る見込みですが……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It should take about half a day...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あ、ちょっと待ってください。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ah, please wait a moment.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ……じゃあ千鶴子様、お願いします
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: ...Then, Lady Chizuruko, please.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: はいはい。じゃあ、このコンピュータ借りるわね
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Alright, then. I'll borrow this computer.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: へ？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Huh?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 千鶴子が触れたコンピュータが、猛然と動き始める。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The computer Chizuruko touched began moving fiercely.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 人の目には留まらない速度で表と数字が入力され、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Tables and numbers were entered at an eye-blink speed,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: それが整えられていく。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and they were organized.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 情報魔法……！　あの量のデータが、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Information magic...! All that data,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 全部あの中に……？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: is all inside that...?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: す、すご……すごいです……！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: A-amazing... It's incredible...!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ゼス全土の現状の情報が、丸ごと入って……！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: All the current information of the entire Zeth territory is fully contained...!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: （でも……それにしても……）
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: (But... even so...)

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: はい、こんなもんかな。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Alright, that should do it.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 古いデータも更新しといたわ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I also updated the old data.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 助かります。では……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Thank you. Well then...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: おっ、千鶴子じゃないか
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Oh, isn't that Chizuruko?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あら総統。失礼していますね
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Oh, Supreme Commander. Sorry for the intrusion.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: それはいいが……相変わらず変な服だな。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: That's fine, but... you're still wearing weird clothes.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 美人がぶち壊しだぞ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It's ruining your beauty.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あっ……！
しっ……しっつれいね、この男は！　相変わらず！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: T-t-tso rude, this man! As always!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: この服は私のデザインなのよーーーー！！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: These clothes are my designーーー!!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: がはははは、ギンギラギンではないか。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Gahahahaha, they're flashy, aren't they?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 美人なんだから脱げ脱げ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You're beautiful, so just take them off already.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: お黙んなさい！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Shut up!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: おじさま……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Uncle...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 言わないでおいたのに……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I had planned not to say anything...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔法の国、ゼス――――
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The magical country, Zethーーー

translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: My body sinks involuntarily.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 口元まで、心地よい湯の中に沈んでいく。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I sink into the pleasant water up to my mouth.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ………………ばかもの
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: ...Fool.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ぶくぶくと泡立つ音に紛れて、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Muddled within the bubbling sound,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: その呟きは夜気に消えていった。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: That whisper vanished into the night air.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 仕方ないか。では、私も前線に出るわね
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It can’t be helped. Then, I’ll head to the front lines as well.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: こんにちは。失礼するわね
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Hello. Excuse me.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あ、千鶴子様。いらっしゃいませ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ah, Lady Chizuruko. Welcome.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あっ……あの方……山田千鶴子さん、ですよね？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ah... That person... is Yamada Chizuruko, right?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: そうですね。ゼス四天王筆頭……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: That's right. The leader of the Zeth Four Heavenly Kings...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ゼスの内政、軍事、外交全てを司る、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The one who controls Zeth's internal affairs, military, and diplomacy,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 事実上の頂点……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The de facto pinnacle...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: こっちの資料、運んできたわよ。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I brought these materials over here.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 国内情勢と軍の現状、それにゼスに来てる
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The domestic situation and current state of the military, plus the status of demon troops in Zeth,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔軍の状況分析
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: an analysis of the demon army's status.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 助かります。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: That helps a lot.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 千鶴子様にわざわざ来てもらってすみません
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Sorry for making Lady Chizuruko come all the way here.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 私がやった方が最終的に手間が省けるから。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It's ultimately less work if I do it myself.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ……今日はこのままとんぼ返りだけど
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: ...But today I'll just make a quick return trip like this.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ありがとうございます……お疲れ様です
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Thank you... and good work.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 苦笑しあう二人の後ろでは、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Behind the two sharing a wry smile,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 紙が満載された大量の箱が、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Boxes brimming with paper,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ゼス兵たちによって次から次へと運び込まれていく。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: were carried in one after another by Zeth soldiers.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: すみません、ウルザ殿。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Excuse me, Lord Urza.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 頂いた資料、処理に掛かって宜しいでしょうか。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: May I begin processing the materials you provided?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 半日ほどで出来る見込みですが……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It should take about half a day...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あ、ちょっと待ってください。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Ah, please wait a moment.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ……じゃあ千鶴子様、お願いします
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: ...Then, Lady Chizuruko, please.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: はいはい。じゃあ、このコンピュータ借りるわね
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Alright, then. I'll borrow this computer.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: へ？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Huh?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 千鶴子が触れたコンピュータが、猛然と動き始める。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The computer Chizuruko touched began moving fiercely.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 人の目には留まらない速度で表と数字が入力され、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Tables and numbers were entered at an eye-blink speed,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: それが整えられていく。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: and they were organized.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 情報魔法……！　あの量のデータが、
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Information magic...! All that data,

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 全部あの中に……？
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: is all inside that...?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: す、すご……すごいです……！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: A-amazing... It's incredible...!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: ゼス全土の現状の情報が、丸ごと入って……！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: All the current information of the entire Zeth territory is fully contained...!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: （でも……それにしても……）
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: (But... even so...)

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: はい、こんなもんかな。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Alright, that should do it.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 古いデータも更新しといたわ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I also updated the old data.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 助かります。では……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Thank you. Well then...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: おっ、千鶴子じゃないか
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Oh, isn't that Chizuruko?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あら総統。失礼していますね
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Oh, Supreme Commander. Sorry for the intrusion.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: それはいいが……相変わらず変な服だな。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: That's fine, but... you're still wearing weird clothes.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 美人がぶち壊しだぞ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: It's ruining your beauty.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: あっ……！
しっ……しっつれいね、この男は！　相変わらず！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: T-t-tso rude, this man! As always!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: この服は私のデザインなのよーーーー！！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: These clothes are my designーーー!!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: がはははは、ギンギラギンではないか。
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Gahahahaha, they're flashy, aren't they?

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 美人なんだから脱げ脱げ
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: You're beautiful, so just take them off already.

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: お黙んなさい！
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Shut up!

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: おじさま……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: Uncle...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 言わないでおいたのに……
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: I had planned not to say anything...

translationLines.originalJapaneseLine: 魔法の国、ゼス――――
translationLines.translatedEnglishLine: The magical country, Zethーーー
